<div id="block-block-203" class="block block-blockblue-free block-last blue-free">
  <h2>Young Scholars Initiative</h2>

  <div class="content">
    <p><a href="ysi" rel="nofollow"><img alt="" src="/sites/inet.civicactions.net/files/HK_YSI_WKSHP_SLIDE_FINAL.jpg" style="width:300px; height:174px" /></a></p>
<p>The <strong><a href="ysi" rel="nofollow">Young Scholars Initiative (YSI)</a></strong><span>&nbsp;is an international community of new economic thinkers comprised of students, young professionals, and researchers, supported by the Institute for New Economic Thinking.</span></p>
<p>We envision economic thinking free of intellectual barriers that resonates with reality and serves our global society.</p>
<ul>
<li>
		<a href="http://ineteconomics.org/ysi/events"><strong>Join&nbsp;Events &amp; Workshops</strong></a></li>
<li>
		<strong><a href="http://www.facebook.com/groups/378629278823493/" rel="nofollow">Join the YSI Facebook Group</a></strong></li>
</ul>
  </div>
